OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder to have case reviewed
OL,6,FA man who spent 36 years in prison for
OL,7,Fthe brutal murder of a betting shop
OL,8,Fmanager he says he did not commit has
OL,9,Fbeen given fresh hope at clearing his
OL,10,Fname.
OL,12,FRay Gilbert, 66, was convicted of
OL,13,Fstabbing John Suffield Junior 19 times
OL,14,Fat the Coral Racing Shop, on Lodge
OL,15,FLane, Toxteth, in what was believed to
OL,16,Fhave been a botched robbery in 1981.
