OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder to have case reviewed
OL,6,FSpeaking to Granada Reports in June
OL,7,F2025, Mr Gilbert said: "I want to
OL,8,Fprove my innocence. I want to be able
OL,9,Fto hold my head up high.
OL,11,F"It's nothing to do about money, I
OL,12,Fjust want my innocence proven.
OL,14,F"You can't let one out and then say
OL,15,Fthe evidence is ok, when the appeal
OL,16,Fcourt's already ruled the evidence is
OL,17,Fuseless."
OL,19,FIn June, ITV Granada Reports presenter
OL,20,FKatie Walderman spoke to Ray about his
OL,21,Fstory.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
