OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder to have case reviewed
OL,6,FHis case will first be looked at by a
OL,7,FCase Review Manager, who will then
OL,8,Fpass on their findings to a group of
OL,9,FCommissioners who will then make a
OL,10,Fdecision on the outcome of Mr
OL,11,FGilbert's request.
OL,13,FThe CCRC has said they "may" be able
OL,14,Fto pass the case to the Commissioners
OL,15,Ffor a decision by the end of 2025.
OL,17,FThis is only the latest of a number of
OL,18,Fattempts from Mr Gilbert to overturn
OL,19,Fhis conviction, but this time he has
OL,20,Fthe support of independent
OL,21,Finvestigator Stephanie Davis.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
