OL,3,CMan who served 36 years in jail for
OL,4,Cmurder to have case reviewed
OL,6,FMr Gilbert's team say there is
OL,7,Fevidence which proves Mr Gilbert could
OL,8,Fnot have committed the crime.
OL,10,FHayley Wood, a Miscarriage of Justice
OL,11,FAdvocate, who is also working on Ray's
OL,12,Fbehalf said: "It's within these
OL,13,Fdocuments we have found certain
OL,14,Finformation that suggests that Ray was
OL,15,Fcertainly not in the place that he was
OL,16,Fforced to confess to where he was.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
